d super secure","Content":"Harrogate Storage Solutions have been brilliant throughout my time spent storing goods with them. Michelle has been helpful and accommodating from day 1. I was even able to make use of their van to move my goods across from my old workplace to my unit at HSS. The units are spotless, dry and super secure. I would highly recommend them and will definitely use again if I need to int he future. Thanks!","Author":"Sean Knott","createdAt":"2022-02-15T15:19:23.074Z","updatedAt":"2022-02-15T15:19:23.711Z","publishedAt":"2022-02-15T15:19:23.710Z","Date":"2020-07-16"}},{"id":30,"attributes":{"Title":"I would always, without hesitation recommend Harrogate Storage Solutions","Content":"I have used Harrogate Storage Solutions for both long term, business, and short term, personal. The service I have received has been exceptional. Nothing seems to be a problem for them and always happy to help. I would always, without hesitation recommend Harrogate Storage Solutions to anyone needing this kind of service.","Author":"Chris Arnold","createdAt":"2022-02-15T15:18:56.708Z","updatedAt":"2022-02-15T15:18:57.294Z","publishedAt":"2022-02-15T15:18:57.293Z","Date":"2020-06-02"}},{"id":29,"attributes":{"Title":"Very useful complementary van","Content":"Great service. Really helpful and quick to respond. The van that’s available to borrow is really helpful","Author":"Daniel Ward","createdAt":"2022-02-15T15:18:32.722Z","updatedAt":"2022-02-15T15:18:33.226Z","publishedAt":"2022-02-15T15:18:33.226Z","Date":"2019-11-14"}},{"id":27,"attributes":{"Title":"Friendly and helpful","Content":"Thanks for everything. The storage unit and access was perfect for our needs, and everyone has been friendly and helpful.","Author":"Michael Domstead","createdAt":"2022-02-15T15:17:55.915Z","updatedAt":"2022-02-15T15:17:56.432Z","publishedAt":"2022-02-15T15:17:56.431Z","Date":"2019-10-05"}},{"id":28,"attributes":{"Title":"Smooth process","Content":"This is a great storage company in Harro